This is a WIP


Basic
~~~~~

* To build jenkins docker role:

cd jenkins; docker build --rm --tag=jenkins .

* Image history

docker history jenkins

* To run jenkins:

INSTANCE_ID=$(docker run -d jenkins)

* To check what is going on:

docker ps

* Inspect a running container (get ip):

docker inspect ${INSTANCE_ID}

* Inspect container sf change:

docker diff ${INSTANCE_ID}




Network
~~~~~~~

* Make sure host is well configured:
sysctl -w net.ipv4.ip_forward=1
sysctl -w net.ipv4.conf.all.route_localnet=1


